quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Yemwe bahakanyi!"
  109,2,"Singaragira ibyo mugaragira,"
  109,3,"Kandi namwe ntimugaragira uwo ngaragira."
  109,4,"Ndetse nanjye sinzigera ngaragira ibyo mugaragira,"
  109,5,"Kandi namwe ntimuzigera mugaragira uwo ngaragira."
  109,6,"Mufite idini ryanyu, nanjye nkagira idini ryanjye.”"
